high_descs: Go around the right side of the counter and stove to the counter to the right of the sink.
Get the knife that is on the counter to the right of the sink.
Move slightly to the left to be in front of the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn around and cross the room to the fridge.
Put the knife along the front edge of the front of the shelf, in front of the tomatoes and close the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Pick up the nearest slice of potato.
Go back to the fridge.
Put the potato slice on the front left corner of the fridge shelf, close the fridge, then open it and take the potato slice back out and close the fridge again.
Carry the potato slice back to the sink.
Put the potato slice in the right front corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato in a sink, leaving the slicing knife in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left then right at the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife inside. then close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Open the fridge and put the potato inside then close the door. Wait a second the open the door and remove the potato. Close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Put the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a refridgerated potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, then left and head towards the sink.
Take the knife from the counter by the sink.
Turn left, then face the sink to the right.
Cut the potato in the sink.
Turn around and head towards the fridge in front of you.
Put the knife inside the fridge and close it.
Turn around and head towards the sink in front of you.
Take a potato slice from the sink.
Turn around and head to the fridge in front of you.
Put the potato slice inside, take the potato slice out and close the fridge.
Turn around and head to the sink in front of you.
Put the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge, go forward to the sink.
Take the knife from the counter to the right of the sink.
Move a step to the left and face the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge.
Put the knife on the lowest shelf of the fridge.
Turn around, go forward to the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge.
Chill the potato on the lower left shelf of the fridge to the left of the tomato. Take the potato from the fridge.
Turn around, go forward to the sink.
Put the potato to the right of the right egg in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato in a sink.
